mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢玩Walking dead應該就係佢既全盛時期<br />\n<br />\nbtw，屌你有dead space back up？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢玩deadsapce好撚好睇，呢套戲係唯一我覺得好撚好睇而佢del左既gameplay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\nwalking dead我好似睇左幾集冇睇<br />\n等我睇埋paper please再睇<br />\n不過佢好多片del左都好可惜<br />\n<br />\n有d係佢自己覺得唔滿意而del,然後又會拍過,試問有幾多香港youtuber拍gameplay會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但有d好似係版權問題"},{"pid":"790f9d56181e6b7f90d8899ef8f32c26e6d6b992","tid":437173,"uid":82889,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T18:48:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>條垃圾都有人吹捧了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家多小學雞上LIHKG 冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小學雞乜撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n伍公子同eminleo同期出既,除左乞耳機叫觀眾捐錢之外真係唔見得有咩問題<br />\n再加上而家比錢實況主/youtuber已經完全唔係一件出奇既事<br />\n你呢d柒頭皮乖乖地番去訓覺啦</blockquote><br />\n講真叫觀眾捐錢呢件事都係無問題，唔撚好比啲小學雞盲反撚影響到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人講佢地又跟著講以為自己好撚有point</blockquote><br />\n講真啦,拍片都要搵食架<br />\n我自己都有學過下電影,一條片雖然就咁睇可能廿幾三十分鐘就出到,但伍公子係會覺得拍得唔好再拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋佢又會做research,唔係剩係拍黎做反應比觀眾睇<br />\n加上佢仲有好多精華片.有試過剪片都知剪一剪都幾粒鐘<br />\n好過咩大j直接放條兩個鐘既gameplay上黎一百倍啦"},{"pid":"f57128e1944f3bbb92e02544a4136729f2ff9a1b","tid":437173,"uid":21772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T18:56:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>tomb raider 笑到仆街</blockquote><br />\n臨尾卡關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14211f26173b86add707a434679288b218228ec